{"tid":89931,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"GH60 機械鍵盤組裝 DIY “Zealio 紫軸 + 鋁殼”（圖多慎入）","createTime":"2017-01-21T16:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T08:23:02.000Z","uid":49000,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61fe53296086667a727739d76b29db35dacb0d76","tid":89931,"uid":49000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"由於時間關係（誤）⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9TUZx5B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9TUZx5B.jpg&h=8bde8be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n工具、材料：<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/8QNbOhx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8QNbOhx.jpg&h=f9e24aff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/CQey0mZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCQey0mZ.jpg&h=4e47005f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n軸體（Zealios tactile 67g &amp; 78g ) x61+<br />\nPCB 衛星軸（四組 2x + 一組 6.25x）<br />\n辣雞、錫線、Cut 鉗、螺絲批、潤滑油脂、去焊錫松脂嘅 Cleaner<br />\n他錶、吸錫泵同膠紙係備用<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/af057Zc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Faf057Zc.jpg&h=52c30f5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雞蛋六隻，糖呢就兩茶匙，仲有啲橙皮添⋯⋯<br />\nGH60 PCB、定位板（今次用碳纖）、外殼<br />\n <br />\n開工：<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/vdeYmOI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvdeYmOI.jpg&h=ef216a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先裝衛星軸<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/GevsUdj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGevsUdj.jpg&h=17a24567&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/yITroLg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyITroLg.jpg&h=b6521b61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/MSAMYwK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMSAMYwK.jpg&h=c209ee6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加神油，裝平衡桿<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fNdHqpZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfNdHqpZ.jpg&h=ca41740e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n定位板對位放上去，裝幾粒軸 hold 住位置<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0kLrRL0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0kLrRL0.jpg&h=4265853b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UyhkVDr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUyhkVDr.jpg&h=8947aad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n焊接點，再陸續裝其他軸，個人習慣二分法每次空位中間裝一兩粒軸然後焊接，咁做軸同板受力平均啲<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/VIWYLMS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVIWYLMS.jpg&h=4d17fc3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/iQvVjDY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiQvVjDY.jpg&h=311dc39b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ydFqzqS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FydFqzqS.jpg&h=24bf1526&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jenn0ne.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fjenn0ne.jpg&h=798a082c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n殼底裝上負重 Plate，之後裝上焊好嘅鍵盤內膽，螺絲先不上緊，放正對齊位然後對邊續口上緊<br />\n <br />\n搞掂飲杯茶，然後繼上鍵帽：<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Mq1mbUJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMq1mbUJ.jpg&h=4343cd84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/CE0yVCG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCE0yVCG.jpg&h=ef55e8f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/bV4dIi3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbV4dIi3.jpg&h=39f744c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/v38YXvK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fv38YXvK.jpg&h=7761383b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/C8PI5EI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FC8PI5EI.jpg&h=4ef507d6&s={SIZE}\" />[img][/img]<br />\n <br />\n多謝收看並多多指教<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/C8PI5EI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FC8PI5EI.jpg&h=4ef507d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9TUZx5B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9TUZx5B.jpg&h=8bde8be4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41a86e859ca4bea5cae529b05d1c690fccb18ba7","tid":89931,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:58:17.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75a734cb41a58ecce79265a742d756160a87b76","tid":89931,"uid":24940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T00:23:53.000Z","msg":"太多Lube，耐左Stabilizer 會變到好鈍。<br />\nLube其實落好少好薄就夠，特別係Grease Lube。"},{"pid":"4234db4ef22ed939c25b4383ed01928e0401b94c","tid":89931,"uid":22571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T00:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太多Lube，耐左Stabilizer 會變到好鈍。<br />\nLube其實落好少好薄就夠，特別係Grease Lube。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪淨係落個個位就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130ffca6fb1ca307a733ee573e61bf13a07f0279","tid":89931,"uid":49000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T01:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太多Lube，耐左Stabilizer 會變到好鈍。<br />\nLube其實落好少好薄就夠，特別係Grease Lube。</blockquote><br />\n下次注意噃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6e4f4fd10feb80924cd00ec9f606abb58cd025","tid":89931,"uid":63549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T02:21:34.000Z","msg":"靚殼靚軸靚板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n少少問題：PCB反而係最大路嘅GH60?"},{"pid":"2eb164817be471c62dd40945709718e6800cd0d3","tid":89931,"uid":3675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT